tem_assets/steam/apps/2409260/extras/690704ec8cb3cf2913453834a82ecbda.webm?t=1736344253\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2409260/extras/690704ec8cb3cf2913453834a82ecbda.mp4?t=1736344253\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXTERMINATE THE ALIEN THREAT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Agents are on the hunt. Their EMF Readers point them towards Mannequins, but telling friend from foe is down to instinct. Not only is ammunition limited, but shooting a human jams your gun, giving Mannequins an opportunity to strike.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2409260/extras/b484b153b9ea2389edc45b9a926d864d.poster.avif?t=1736344253\" width=600 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2409260/extras/b484b153b9ea2389edc45b9a926d864d.webm?t=1736344253\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2409260/extras/b484b153b9ea2389edc45b9a926d864d.mp4?t=1736344253\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WORK TOGETHER, DIE ALONE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Teamwork is essential. Strategize to seize energy extractors as aliens, letting you see an Agent’s location. If you’re not fast enough, Agents gain the upper hand.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2409260/extras/8e2a11c43d99b77732480e332fa9335d.poster.avif?t=1736344253\" width=600 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2409260/extras/8e2a11c43d99b77732480e332fa9335d.webm